caller_intent: The caller (Tracy Carver) needs to add a newly purchased vehicle to her insurance policy and retrieve her policy number for the update.
resolution_steps: Agent Heather confirms the caller's name and purpose of the call.
Heather acknowledges the request to add a vehicle and retrieves policy information.
Heather states she will transfer the call to another agent to assist with the policy update.
knowledge_required: Process for adding vehicles to existing policies
summary: Tracy Carver contacted Alliance Insurance to add a new vehicle to her policy and obtain her policy number. Agent Heather confirmed the request and initiated a transfer to another agent for further assistance. The call was not resolved in this interaction but was directed to appropriate support.
